[[File:AntinnisTremayne-TCG.png|thumb|right|250px|High Inquisitor Antinnis Tremayne]]
'''High Inquisitor''' was a senior rank in the [[Inquisitorius/Legends|Inquisitorius]], a shadowy branch of [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence]] consisting of [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]] [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitives]] [[Agent/Legends|agents]] who worked under the command of [[Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] himself. They were often employed as interrogators, though their primary task was to seek out potential [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] candidates and investigate [[The Force/Legends|Force activity]] during the [[Imperial Era/Legends|reign]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. The only higher rank in the Inquisitorius was that of [[Grand Inquisitor/Legends|Grand Inquisitor]], who was the head of the Inquisitorius. After the fall of the Empire, many of the surviving Inquisitors joined the [[Great InQuestor of Judgment]].

